e turn of the eighteenth century.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 0aHaskalah. 0aJewish philosophy. 4aJewish Studies. 4aReligion -- Judaism. 7aRELIGION / Judaism / History.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertStanford University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z97831107042040 cprintz978080475136040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9780804767682?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804767682423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780804767682/original  a978-3-11-070420-4  Stanford University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles